                  </hi>. I am landlord of the house, 5, Ebor-ferrace, Stoke</p>
               <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="186305110111"></xptr>
               <p>Newington—I recollect the prisoner coming there in the month of February last, but not the day—on the morning of the 24th I went into Mr. Turner's room—I had not seen the prisoner that morning.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
