                  </hi>. I am assistant to Mr. Smith, of Tottenham-court-road, pawnbroker—I produce a coat which was pledged on 16th February in the name of "John Coventry"—I cannot recollect whether prisoner is the man.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
